dc_title_s: West Indies, Cuba--south coast, Cayo Miguel to Cayo Blanco (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From Cuban charts to 1976." "Copyright 1995 by the United States government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes compilation diagram. Map No.27161 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
